\n剩係識問錢錢錢<br />\n<br />\n另一次就係我生日<br />\n我男朋友送咗ipad比我<br />\n返到屋企我老母見到問係咪佢送<br />\n一聽到話係佢送即刻又扮哂嘢咁話<br />\n🧑🏻&zwj;🦰：咁我呢，佢唔洗送嘢比我㗎？我部電話都就黎壞，唔係應該要送嘢比我嘅咩<br />\n我聽到已經即刻話 <br />\n下，點解要送比你<br />\n<br />\n個老母剩係識睇錢好辛苦<br />\n雖然我同男朋友拍拖係我地兩個人嘅事<br />\n但如果佢一路咁樣唔同意又咁市儈最後唔通又要反哂面咁咩<br />\n有時真係唔明啲父母諗咩<br />\n有錢又唔等於對你好 點解睇到錢咁重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:49:07.000Z","msg":"我Ex 個呀媽同你呀媽性格一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n忍唔到"},{"pid":"c7fe18209b8bf1c7eb62671d768671af773f3bd9","tid":2245550,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"d3e311c3e90072e90f858cd4a9d564fb1613283e","tid":2245550,"uid":378305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:52:13.000Z","msg":"你老母想當你係私家性奴賣比有錢仔，而唔係當你係人咁嫁比人"},{"pid":"2b0069facbbf485ff35785d29a795e2b1df56b76","tid":2245550,"uid":49015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d97385383dfa771106e58a54c3a6543d397cd05","tid":2245550,"uid":38122,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錢仔中出即飛啦"},{"pid":"4cc3da6dd935fa7a35f137bc9fbd7d7d4d5023b5","tid":2245550,"uid":368767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"點解咁撚鍾意喺Dcard cop人篇文再po 出來"},{"pid":"610088c9fa1dee59aa06d9deb031d1f0ffeaf920","tid":2245550,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得你老豆應該慘過你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40ce30f9eb3ae65050d19d093433cd2ee93613d"