0-10-16T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"好快你就會同條仔分手<br />\n<br />\n佢會識到個更加好嘅女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83cba914fb4d72efd252691e2f21160969959de","tid":2245550,"uid":265628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"通常都係潛意識反射.<br />\n呢個時間你可以比你媽媽攬下.<br />\n跟住同佢講: 乖啦,你老公系個到. 老豆叫你呀!!<br />\n再同佢講: 你失敗過一次,我明既."},{"pid":"69e84eabbae63f7b7c11d7cd8759cc392ce06121","tid":2245550,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"答佢：你咁想嫁俾個有錢人你又唔嫁？你做唔撚到嘅嘢唔好要求你下一代做到"},{"pid":"c4cc72a30d62766c7672b430ea53afee369a4ff7","tid":2245550,"uid":24745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6295506a21db6df8d09eebdaa4304dbba0576e8","tid":2245550,"uid":176650,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>🧑🏻&zwj;🦰：咁我呢，佢唔洗送嘢比我㗎？我部電話都就黎壞，唔係應該要送嘢比我嘅咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cls 唔講仲以為你老母同你男朋友拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"咁撚似5仔既<br />\n見bob叔送mac book俾周庭<br />\n就話bob叔點解唔送支咪俾佢 肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aca332e7a79ff777cd793eed19523b1fcfabc0c","tid":2245550,"uid":184932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1c690bf51692ce0a9d7845f4c245b8fb4f1452ec","tid":2245550,"uid":230197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得我老母好市儈所以唔想比佢知我拍拖<br />\n但拍咗幾年唔想成日講大話瞞住 好辛苦<br />\n所以同我老母講咗我拍拖<br />\n點知佢一開口關心嘅嘢全部都係錢<br />\n一黎就問我佢住邊<br />\n又話下又揾個住公屋嘅（但我地都係住公屋）<br />\n跟住就係咁問收入 問返咩<br />\n然後就話<br />\n🧑🏻&zwj;🦰：我好唔滿意囉，佢做呢啲工又住公屋 bababa....<br />\n然後講到明叫我唔好諗住同佢結婚 拍下拖就好<br />\n成個過程係無關心過我地點識 一齊咗幾耐 佢對我好唔好<br />\n剩係識問錢錢錢<br />\n<br />\n另一次就係我生日<br />\n我男朋友送咗ipad比我<br />\n返到屋企我老母見到問係咪佢送<br />\n一聽到話係佢送即刻又扮哂嘢咁話<br />\n🧑🏻&zwj;🦰：咁我呢，佢唔洗送嘢比我㗎？我部電話都就黎壞，唔係應該要送嘢比我嘅咩<br />\n我聽到已經即刻話 <br />\n下，點解要送比你<br />\n<br />\n個老母剩係識睇錢好辛苦<br />\n雖然我同男朋友拍拖係我地兩個人嘅事<br />\n但如果佢一路咁樣唔同意又咁市儈最後唔通又要反哂面咁咩<br />\n有時真係唔明啲父母諗咩<br />\n有錢又唔等於對你好 點解睇到錢咁重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"*你嫁個公屋仔<br />\n第時生活兩個都手緊<br />\n邊個養你老母本人*<br />\n<br />\n養兒防老心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9ef7fa84022c0a8e66fe825ca8c0fb1d9e9821","tid":2245550,"uid":49302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:29:44.000Z","msg":"假膠post 就上熱門, 連燈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b7fee22574ea687c189bc270192b3120dd8312","tid":2245550,"uid":195211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:30:07.000Z","msg":"公屋仔先正"},{"pid":"78641cdaf4320d1e60234e12dd7f573cd32de02c","tid":2245550,"uid":260296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\nBan <br />\n上頁"},{"pid":"eeef09ddcaa7362a7e34cd1c91bd2cddae932880","tid":2245550,"uid":60082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"咁似我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我既選擇係一早就兩個人搬出去住<br />\n唔洗俾佢煩 日日都話邊個親戚朋友啲女個老公幾有錢帶拹全家<br />\n又話蠢點解唔揀下 好煩"},{"pid":"04e9927e12a0ede9982d710a488df250fea020e4","tid":2245550,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d94daddd075cacc702805516803aac893db5714a","tid":2245550,"uid":215853,"like":267,"dislike":1,"score":266,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"起底 此post 完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:38:19.000Z","msg":"thx"},{"pid":"ff8259a0a3c29b7bf90998e02442263be5983222","tid":2245550,"uid":275009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c690b